  "detailed_description": "Welcome a new member of C.A.S.T. (CHERNOZEM ANOMALY STRIKE TEAM)<br><br>Dive into an alternate 1950s Europe in this co-op third-person extraction shooter. Combining advanced technology with a nostalgic twist, your squad will confront monstrous threats and anomalies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/1cbff27ae68867fd3a0052d04a27b712.poster.avif?t=1752481894\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/1cbff27ae68867fd3a0052d04a27b712.webm?t=1752481894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/1cbff27ae68867fd3a0052d04a27b712.mp4?t=1752481894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/ec8bab2ee0b348c6978f85f98403ca74.webp?t=1752481894\" width=604 height=46 /></span><br>Whether playing solo or in co-op (1-4 players), experience dynamic gameplay with unique objectives and challenging side tasks. Your success relies on precise teamwork and strategy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/bb1dabcaf0dea756bdd3440a77cfc1ae.webp?t=1752481894\" width=604 height=46 /></span><br>Venture through handcrafted maps enhanced with procedural elements and varied weather conditions. Each map features distinct objectives and random anomalies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/b26b34edcee101c34e9e98537577ce42.webp?t=1752481894\" width=604 height=46 /></span><br>Equip a wide array of ranged and melee weapons, each with upgrade options. Create and refine your loadout with unique modifiers, and utilize the crafting workshop to enhance your existing gear and craft new ones.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/1a9f1ff471e9a201dcf2eee022c3199e.webp?t=1752481894\" width=604 height=46 /></span><br>Face off against a variety of distinct enemies, each with their own strengths and tactics. Adapt your strategies to survive their attacks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/d3ada455703fb618a99986fc8681efba.poster.avif?t=1752481894\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/d3ada455703fb618a99986fc8681efba.webm?t=1752481894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/d3ada455703fb618a99986fc8681efba.mp4?t=1752481894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Welcome a new member of C.A.S.T. (CHERNOZEM ANOMALY STRIKE TEAM)<br><br>Dive into an alternate 1950s Europe in this co-op third-person extraction shooter. Combining advanced technology with a nostalgic twist, your squad will confront monstrous threats and anomalies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/1cbff27ae68867fd3a0052d04a27b712.poster.avif?t=1752481894\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/1cbff27ae68867fd3a0052d04a27b712.webm?t=1752481894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/1cbff27ae68867fd3a0052d04a27b712.mp4?t=1752481894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/ec8bab2ee0b348c6978f85f98403ca74.webp?t=1752481894\" width=604 height=46 /></span><br>Whether playing solo or in co-op (1-4 players), experience dynamic gameplay with unique objectives and challenging side tasks. Your success relies on precise teamwork and strategy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/bb1dabcaf0dea756bdd3440a77cfc1ae.webp?t=1752481894\" width=604 height=46 /></span><br>Venture through handcrafted maps enhanced with procedural elements and varied weather conditions. Each map features distinct objectives and random anomalies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/b26b34edcee101c34e9e98537577ce42.webp?t=1752481894\" width=604 height=46 /></span><br>Equip a wide array of ranged and melee weapons, each with upgrade options. Create and refine your loadout with unique modifiers, and utilize the crafting workshop to enhance your existing gear and craft new ones.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/1a9f1ff471e9a201dcf2eee022c3199e.webp?t=1752481894\" width=604 height=46 /></span><br>Face off against a variety of distinct enemies, each with their own strengths and tactics. Adapt your strategies to survive their attacks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/d3ada455703fb618a99986fc8681efba.poster.avif?t=1752481894\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/d3ada455703fb618a99986fc8681efba.webm?t=1752481894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140620/extras/d3ada455703fb618a99986fc8681efba.mp4?t=1752481894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
